Tim Tebow , 27 , hasn't played a snap in the NFL since being cut by the New England Patriots before the 2013 season . 
  The Philadelphia Eagles officially signed the quarterback to a one-year contract on Monday . 
  Tebow was the 2007 Heisman Trophy winner at Florida . 
  He was a first-round draft choice of the Denver Broncos in 2010 but was cut in 2013 . 
  He has not played in a regular season game since 2012 with the New York Jets . 
 